Package fixlib

Class Fixlib

  • java.lang.Object
    • fixlib.Fixlib
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PConstants
    public final class Fixlib
extends java.lang.Object
implements PConstants
    FixLib is your new utility library. House all your helper code here, and keep the main sketch.pde as light as possible ( setup, draw, exit, artDaily ) NOTE: code dates to 2012 - a lot of "app." code in here, can't be a big static lib

        public PShape shapeJous​(float a,
                        float b,
                        float amp,
                        int inc)
        Lissajous PShape maker
        Parameters:
        a - X coordinate
        b - Y coordinate
        amp - Amplitude or size
        inc - Loop magic incrementer [ 1 - 36 supported ]. (360 / inc) = number of points in returned PShape
        Returns:
        PShape containing vertices in the shape of a lissajous pattern
